&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;                    禅定时刻&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;羚羊宝宝问羚羊妈妈：“为什么我们整天走来走去，跑来跑去，努力吃草，而猎豹他们却在我们努力的时候公然躺在树荫下睡懒觉？” &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;羚羊妈妈说：“有些动物就是看不惯你努力的样子，总会想方设法干扰你。多数动物都是懒散的，他们觉得那才是常态，而一个努力向上的羚羊，身上的光芒会让庸众恐惧。所以想想看，奋斗者是最孤独的，你必得隔绝身边一些扰耳的声音，才能心无旁骛的去成功。  ” &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;猎豹宝宝听到了，就去问猎豹妈妈：“妈妈，这头食物在说什么呢？” &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;猎豹妈妈说：“她一辈子吃草，就把努力吃草看得比什么都重要，觉得有草吃就是莫大成功，把我们躺在树荫下休息视为十恶不赦。而她永远也弄不明白一件事情，我们猎豹之所以休息那么长时间，是因为我们吃肉不吃草。我们每天只出击三次，努力保证33.3%的成功率。如果我们也像她吃草那样努力，要么是我们累死，要么是我们一天之内就把他们全都杀光。” &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;说完，猎豹妈妈伏低身体，在草丛中潜行。羚羊妈妈正口若悬河地对孩子讲演，等发现猎豹的时候，猎豹已经进入最高速度冲刺。虽然羚羊妈妈转身就跑，中途还做了两次变线，但最后还是成为了猎豹家的晚餐。 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;猎豹妈妈看着吃得正香的孩子，就问：你今天学到了什么？猎豹宝宝嘟嘟囔囔地回答：想吃肉，就得多休息。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;weapp_image_link js_weapp_entry&quot; data-miniprogram-appid=&quot;wxf3e6055a60a19d97&quot; data-miniprogram-path=&quot;pages/home/dashboard/index&quot; data-miniprogram-nickname=&quot;&amp;#x83DC;&amp;#x5934;&amp;#x7279;&amp;#x9009;C&quot; href=&quot;http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/vgjwdJ8x8y&quot; data-miniprogram-type=&quot;image&quot; data-miniprogram-servicetype=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6562054208273894&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/Ia6gU9JNtkribyhn2k4XW55hN2fv5EhBHtzfmiaWRhPicUw9icA9vX3iabZxyAPPHfl3Oia1nhgOsMg82uoY3FLABgVA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;701&quot;/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;点击图片了解松茸牦牛酱，精神生活的基础是物质生活。&lt;/p&gt;
